The Uber guilds have declared that on patch day they in essence do away with the raid calender to take out the bigger boss mobs like Casiz Thule and the other Planes baddies. My old guild has been screwed twice this way because Weds is their normal raid day for Fear. So, everyone who has signed up for their Fear raid (sorry if you have never played EQ, but this is the most appropriate example that's on my mind at the moment) basically either sits around out side the portal waiting for scraps from the larger guild or goes and does something else even though the raid has been scheduled long before the patch was announced. This is what I'm talking about when I say PGs can ruin the fun and play of other ppl in the game.<br>
