<br>
Basically Verant screwed up when buffing the head bosses and letting them drop much desired &quot;uber&quot; gear that 55+ players could use. THat was their fault. The fault of the PGs is to assume that they deserve that loot at the expense of other ppls. It is that reason why I left that game and fear that this game will soon follow with the advent of &quot;uber&quot; loot. <br>
